Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: I was able to enter trades sometimes nonetheless even though balance wasnt really there, so maybe some are trying to connect with people trying to trade with unconfirmed balances. And that should not be possible offcourse!

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: So only logical your trades dont work in that case

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: You dont want to end up trading 10 BTC for whatever amount of kmd if one of both balances is not confirmed...

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content:
So my new gameplan:
1) check if balances are confirmed
2) try trading, put in order that matches the books
3) if trade not matches within 30 secs, remove trade: you are probably trying to match with someone with unconfirmed balance
4) rince and repeat
